{"tid":219552,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"去巴倫紐睇戲真係好似比錢入場食屎","createTime":"2017-04-27T09:50:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-30T08:59:34.000Z","uid":42848,"like":46,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"285eb7a54af5d6426598365490d1828322535a29","tid":219552,"uid":42848,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T09:50:37.000Z","msg":"隔左半年無入巴倫紐，對上果次已經係睇幸運是我，<br />\n如果唔係屯門ua，凱都無上，或者夾唔到時間都唔會去呢間戲院，<br />\n咁呢輪忙左成個月終於抽到時間睇一念無明，<br />\n但見屯門淨返巴倫紐有上就焗住走去睇，<br />\n雖則明知巴倫紐係for溝女消遣用，<br />\n但都無咁離譜掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />入到去個幕上半裂左忽，右邊仲要有條痕，<br />\n跟住銀幕兩邊出口指示位仲著過個銀幕，<br />\n套戲開始左成分鐘先熄大燈，<br />\n左右兩邊觀眾吹水玩電話，隔離院飛車聲仲大聲過曾志偉，<br />\n下次真係除非係獨家放映都唔想再去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b80be71dc91dfb87b55960383cb073d41f7a3e4","tid":219552,"uid":35192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T09:52:12.000Z","msg":"agree"},{"pid":"c24213ec52a9322545f13e5a304d6197d1b27786","tid":219552,"uid":56225,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T09:53:42.000Z","msg":"我覺得幾好喎<br />\n戲飛平過ua一半，買盒叉雞飯入去食都無人理<br />\n係焗少少啫，咪張貨就價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e00c1c17843936b14c5e0afd9b20472840758325","tid":219552,"uid":78222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T09:54:55.000Z","msg":"agger<br />\n同樣價錢凱都真係屈機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n巴倫紐d隔音真係太差 成日聽到隔離擋聿播鬼片/爆炸聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"437821143936fa0ff6f9d6f57b3205c94db74407","tid":219552,"uid":83328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T09:55:15.000Z","msg":"自從n年前傳睇睇下有老鼠就冇幫襯過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好彩睇親都大片, 專揀凱都"},{"pid":"1e97c78d4426e1482d184a85ab37a9e1facc618a","tid":219552,"uid":4723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T09:56:48.000Z","msg":"Exit<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f6b86bded5c96cd0e4e9244e822c7c5ea4ce267","tid":219552,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T09:57:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得幾好喎<br />\n戲飛平過ua一半，買盒叉雞飯入去食都無人理<br />\n係焗少少啫，咪張貨就價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唯一價值係頂死凱都等凱都無得加價，<br />\n但屌佢巴輪紐係睇半年都好意思加5蚊票價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25cec07dac1e5632be0bf3ba327853dcc3ff066d","tid":219552,"uid":3935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T10:04:50.000Z","msg":"反而我唔鍾意去ua, 細個試過去ua 睇死亡筆記佢個畫面有好多&quot;線&quot; 唔知係唔係你講裂左果d, 自從去凱都"},{"pid":"d4c498f799bc2171840a71c2f935a5bfb51a9cb5","tid":219552,"uid":10845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T10:09:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>反而我唔鍾意去ua, 細個試過去ua 睇死亡筆記佢個畫面有好多&quot;線&quot; 唔知係唔係你講裂左果d, 自從去凱都</blockquote><br />\n屯門ua好似好細咁個院，坐後面都好前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29604f343ecfc0ee76c7b6435cb1ac3f06d56f22","tid":219552,"uid":106030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T10:10:50.000Z","msg":"臭你又奶"},{"pid":"6a10d11e041718db9bd7e5e39948569d00d4094e","tid":219552,"uid":1495,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T10:11:08.000Z","msg":"巴倫紐窮人恩物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2904ad6be8b7b4f279e77a1ab7b4895cec59510a","tid":219552,"uid":20302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T10:12:00.000Z","msg":"以前ex住果邊  <br />\n成日去巴黎睇戲 好抵屌  一分錢一分貨"},{"pid":"9a2ff2e23d9bb8c1b7bba6aee32053f6b16c525b","tid":219552,"uid":89485,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T10:14:52.000Z","msg":"巴倫紐啲質素越嚟越差<br />\n個地板仲要好癡嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ba8c6638a3495f1cad7bf2810026db3e7f25791","tid":219552,"uid":83328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T10:15:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴倫紐窮人恩物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n學樓上講<br />\n同樣價錢點解唔揀凱都<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e59607c5f40c76128a771eba59576936f148d811","tid":219552,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T10:15:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴倫紐窮人恩物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n學樓上巴打咁講同票價有凱都，<br />\n貴少少但戲多啲有屯門ua，<br />\n巴倫紐做街坊生意都唔係咁hea掛，<br />\n半年前都無爛幕，而家就一分錢一啖屎，<br />\n豪華戲院好似上年都有裝修啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64efbbabe30b6da5229a3678ecb6c6ea9bc1efdc","tid":219552,"uid":28372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T10:21:05.000Z","msg":"呢排冇去 但So far睇左咁多年都覺得好抵"},{"pid":"7fc31567fef28b899edb6e0327b3088e50530ee2","tid":219552,"uid":90520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T10:26:02.000Z","msg":"屌那星 講起真係嬲嬲地<br />\n巴倫紐真係衰在隔音<br />\n嗰陣睇唔知乜文藝片 愛情片<br />\n總之係少音樂 細聲 架啦<br />\n正當套野係到培養緊氣氛嗰陣<br />\n<br />\n隔離院係到大叫 撞車 死人 冧樓<br />\n屌 乜撚野氣氛都冇撚哂<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過我仍然好鍾意去<br />\n因為佢真係陪住我成長<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n入面有好多回憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同過好幾條女係入面睇過戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec08cb8817c60210085e1bdf005c3da5b65ab5ef","tid":219552,"uid":36157,"l