"5f0b85987359c9d9745944876b2a2333d4c141f4","tid":219552,"uid":64953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T11:15:55.000Z","msg":"凱都冇早場<br />\n要睇早場一係巴倫紐一係UA"},{"pid":"96eb44982599937adb35afbb5c98a482d3d73479","tid":219552,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T11:15:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇一念無名，獎門人同fishmenlok喺天台嗰場戲，突然嘭一聲，隔離院播爆炸場面。咩feel都冇哂。</blockquote><br />\n方晧玫寬恕余文樂可以聽到有飛車聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2e52c12fc5ca1c3c785374c8a3faa704ec9df50","tid":219552,"uid":80297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T11:19:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我上次去UA睇深夜食堂<br />\n隔離恐龍係到跑同叫嘈到過黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n正想講<br />\n同你遭遇一樣<br />\n垃圾屯門UA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"695e03fd7e4db5e1ef5e4353428091d640231cb6","tid":219552,"uid":12596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T11:20:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好似四號院有條好長既裂痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n早幾日喺4號院睇 成條裂痕阻住晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n天花板仲要有條電線吊落嚟遮住個螢幕<br />\n但係真係好平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19dd4732151d1251ab188be89daf8c460417c6ae","tid":219552,"uid":4434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T11:23:15.000Z","msg":"凱都<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e32072e76eb7a5acb509df0d10a6777a1e973dbf","tid":219552,"uid":46373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T11:25:29.000Z","msg":"巴倫紐啲硬件衰啲定豪華衰啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c3499bfc058a4d6677b51a4ea570fd4cf8b1275","tid":219552,"uid":32961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T11:30:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好似四號院有條好長既裂痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n早幾日喺4號院睇 成條裂痕阻住晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n天花板仲要有條電線吊落嚟遮住個螢幕<br />\n但係真係好平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個條唔知電線定乜啦 都有左成半年<br />\n唔知點解有人揀巴倫紐<br />\n配置差 位又窄 音響大但戲院距離又近 下下隔離院都炸到啲聲過黎 爆谷又唔係好食 隔離凱都朱古力爆谷質素拋佢幾條街<br />\n試過一大班fd睇戲 個搞手揀左巴倫紐睇 我去隔離凱都買朱古力爆谷番去巴倫紐食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94e310ab05bf12ef3e7873b81f276f4a01d582ac","tid":219552,"uid":88343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T11:32:41.000Z","msg":"以前都會覺得敦倫紐平靚正，但越睇越唔係路，大部分缺點上都好多人講晒，佢地嘅爆谷最經典<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 買親都一堆爆唔開嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，我直接將爆唔開果Dom落地下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 發生咗呢幾d事之後決定唔再去，凱都冇得睇/唔啱時間嘅話寧願比貴d/出遠d<br />\n<br />\n1.2014年有次睇'毒火追擊'，屌佢開場時間先搣飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上到戲院仲要冇廣告直接播緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原本諗住睇完投訴但可能套戲唔好睇最後冇咗呢個念頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2.有次買完飛想唱埋錢，個售價員係個老女人，佢唔知聽唔明我要求定覺得煩就勁燥咁鬧：姐係點呀？咁煩嫁？個個要散紙嘅話我地就多多都唔夠用嫁啦！'之類嘅野，事後佢仲要嬲住同隔離果個望住我黎話，我果刻原全可以投訴佢，但我果日心情奇好，我全程笑住，比佢Hi完我仲同fd笑住望住佢講返件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n敦倫紐宜家對我來講狗也不屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2bf2135e16f01f3fc8f6d143203ee4b95d3eafb","tid":219552,"uid":85934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T11:36:06.000Z","msg":"去凱都啦"},{"pid":"6b13e33ba929b988f24c8ca8047b8e390b6a59ab","tid":219552,"uid":22270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T11:37:58.000Z","msg