mal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要平既去新寶仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f972155f222e41cdd9cce38790ab4e3ba8c7e145","tid":219552,"uid":16885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T12:21:44.000Z","msg":"凱都屌打晒其他"},{"pid":"078b74fb5cef8d4c81f7c64677064a4769bcf79f","tid":219552,"uid":52405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T12:22:19.000Z","msg":"冇人講影藝？"},{"pid":"53c613793f566111079fd3edbfc6da3aeda5c3b9","tid":219552,"uid":18615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T12:25:13.000Z","msg":"攪到咁，仲衰過係屋企睇碟"},{"pid":"bcef188e1ab7ba971305a699701c3bd4b9f385fd","tid":219552,"uid":26602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T12:35:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>凱都裝修完仲有得輸？</blockquote><br />\n屌打埋屯門UA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nUA又細又凍又貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屯門UA垃圾嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d05aca604d6443d388127a4d4b33509991c10bd","tid":219552,"uid":1403,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T12:36:17.000Z","msg":"個天花板長期有幾條鳩毛吊係度條條揈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搞左幾年都冇人理，唔係其他場爆人我都唔會入去"},{"pid":"fc9fb389c01803f7a5ae21ee6ee519c9726735fa","tid":219552,"uid":24805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T12:40:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴倫紐窮人恩物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n學樓上巴打咁講同票價有凱都，<br />\n貴少少但戲多啲有屯門ua，<br />\n巴倫紐做街坊生意都唔係咁hea掛，<br />\n半年前都無爛幕，而家就一分錢一啖屎，<br />\n豪華戲院好似上年都有裝修啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n華懋做生意方法，正常人唔會理解到<br />\n況且娛樂部想執左佢好耐，點知死剩屯門反而有賺，又由佢繼續<br />\n<br />\n有賺 = 唔落資源 = 殘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9adb2168e3399025788b20a102bafd498e9a159","tid":219552,"uid":30830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T12:41:11.000Z","msg":"過年果排都有去巴倫紐都覺得幾好喎，窮人恩物 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40ef61d5da0a13be22345d499c45ebda7843cea5","tid":219552,"uid":108821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T12:43:17.000Z","msg":"隔音真係好差，其他都接受到"},{"pid":"d8f73fbab151a1e3950d48bb6a05b81ca55643c9","tid":219552,"uid":85787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T12:44:35.000Z","msg":"我試過睇到一半無左字幕，最後退票 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ea6e5b7905c420109d7efd3ff613ef1fc602cec","tid":219552,"uid":12614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T12:48:00.000Z","msg":"凱都好似貴巴倫樓五蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17d33cc20a6a1ebf355345e7d161d188fcd25104","tid":219552,"uid":68073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T12:48:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n1.2014年有次睇'毒火追擊'，屌佢開場時間先搣飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上到戲院仲要冇廣告直接播緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原本諗住睇完投訴但可能套戲唔好睇最後冇咗呢個念頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2.有次買完飛想唱埋錢，個售價員係個老女人，佢唔知聽唔明我要求定覺得煩就勁燥咁鬧：姐係點呀？咁煩嫁？個個要散紙嘅話我地就多多都唔夠用嫁啦！'之類嘅野，事後佢仲要嬲住同隔離果個望住我黎話，我果刻原全可以投訴佢，但我果日心情奇好，我全程笑住，比佢Hi完我仲同fd笑住望住佢講返件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </blockquote><br />\n<br />\n鍵盤戰士唔好搵咁多籍口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3bf5d9e91f58441a38ca5c9a47db649e6d432d1","tid":219552,"uid":88343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T12:50:58.000Z","msg":