> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過我仍然好鍾意去<br />\n因為佢真係陪住我成長<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n入面有好多回憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同過好幾條女係入面睇過戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n陪我成長嗰間係屯門戲院<br />\n嗰陣爆谷味真係唔會忘記"},{"pid":"46b1f35fbd3776eeb1b7002e6a15e9b07bc628fc","tid":219552,"uid":104269,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T13:20:07.000Z","msg":"之前去呢間濕尻戲院，佢話佢哋賣飛果陣標錯價錢，要即場加返錢先俾入去睇，都on撚9"},{"pid":"426cb25fc6da5d849425832df55cadcc89655863","tid":219552,"uid":29299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T13:23:21.000Z","msg":"想當年鍾意既女仔住天水圍<br />\n<br />\n次次都係入屯門同佢去巴倫紐睇戲<br />\n<br />\n但而家無再聯絡喇<br />\n<br />\n佢有男朋友,我都就黎結婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7fcf72792a8bc7d0a3c2ce9bc723ae3e15fd34b","tid":219552,"uid":10434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T13:26:04.000Z","msg":"最記得睇world war z 果陣brad pitt 掉flare, 之後後座同步著火....但大家嘩然完一陣噴熄左記當冇事繼續睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7f2c33a4feee395fafd3ca9e4a1f7fe6c5d96eb","tid":219552,"uid":49768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T13:28:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解我睇咁多次都未試過咁既問題"},{"pid":"20550494bbca525679fd26dd1ff33415a409053b","tid":219552,"uid":1024,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T13:30:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 旺角百老匯都好垃圾"},{"pid":"59d74f948ee97ef1b8a47cd34a35db5b312be63f","tid":219552,"uid":77191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T13:34:52.000Z","msg":"咁平算係咁啦<