587c7b6297756d7c4700555f35","tid":219552,"uid":4723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T15:46:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Exit盞燈真係世界級</blockquote><br />\n宜家轉咗藍燈都好啲<br />\n以前係綠色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30f699fe2972a47380d5e1ed4df6104afa855b8d","tid":219552,"uid":35035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T16:45:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇一念無名，獎門人同fishmenlok喺天台嗰場戲，突然嘭一聲，隔離院播爆炸場面。咩feel都冇哂。</blockquote><br />\n方晧玫寬恕余文樂可以聽到有飛車聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n師兄係咪睇晏就兩點場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dff7749c91168bf5eae81e1e8edfc44f225f2dc","tid":219552,"uid":45943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T17:06:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實好似ua屯門都做埋今年汁粒轉手比嘉禾啦</blockquote><br />\n都有d飛平左好多，又坐得舒服</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n嘉禾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  發夢cinema city進軍屯門"},{"pid":"3068d35fbaebda6d287653bdb5c73d8165cf4d0e","tid":219552,"uid":45943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T17:10:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 旺角百老匯都好垃圾</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n位又唔好坐 入場條隊長到 又要行成幾層<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9270fc3560594509e2455159c0b4b78aa6189d4","tid":219552,"uid":60500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T17:10:47.000Z","msg":"去得巴倫紐睇應該都只係貪佢平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8658d6da287619ed7a1f70b25d21cd0bb6e9b550","tid":219552,"uid":45943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T17:12:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我試過睇到一半無左字幕，最後退票 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n凱都試過未播已經壞機 搞咗大半個鐘先退錢"},{"pid":"18281d6508520ffbff828e439fb16a5a42183a74","tid":219552,"uid":97622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T19:40:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 旺角百老匯都好垃圾</blockquote><br />\n入戲院睇前面個頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe67efd5fafadb793b4a6786a9a22738faf3c77b","tid":219552,"uid":82696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T19:45:28.000Z","msg":"屯門UA執啦就"},{"pid":"f72c608d920b7016713b687b4cea8efb2ca30884","tid":219552,"uid":83328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T09:44:09.000Z","msg":"唔知呢兩間戲院老細點諗? 兩間打正對面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 定係收齊兩家茶禮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋依家唔係巴倫紐，係巴倫紐米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過暫時未聽過人咁叫"},{"pid":"efa701e25090a85a6ecfb257b02de7c435e83923","tid":219552,"uid":39723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T11:28:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屯門UA執啦就</blockquote><br />\n堅？"},{"pid":"05390390bc48932bd2618cd708eb91fc44847668","tid":219552,"uid":10023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T11:38:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇一念無明已經錯晒 就算拍得幾好都好 但搵左憎至矮去拍已經係死罪</blockquote><br />\n首先要知道點解搵至矮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係因為至矮欣賞黃進先做免費演員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fe139844318e3234f11f20a1625ed9683ef1377","tid":219552,"uid":10023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T11:39:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n1.2014年有次睇'毒火追擊'，屌佢開場時間先搣飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上到戲院仲要冇廣告直接播緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原本諗住睇完投訴但可能套戲唔好睇最後冇咗呢個念頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2.有次買完飛想唱埋錢，個售價員係個老女人，佢唔知聽唔明我要求定覺得煩就勁燥咁鬧：姐係點呀？咁煩嫁？個個要散紙嘅話我地就多多都唔夠用嫁啦！'之類嘅野，事後佢仲要嬲住同隔離果個望住我黎話，我果刻原全可以投訴佢，但我果日心情奇好，我全程笑住，比佢Hi完我仲同fd笑住望住佢講返件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </blockquote><br />\n<br />\n鍵盤戰士唔好搵咁多籍口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n話人喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n隔住個moon都feel到陣柒氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1e4e7ea42f115da9f03c7d050fddb8234ae5ad9","tid":219552,"uid":15282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T11:48:56.000Z","msg":"對上個次起巴紐偏睇已經係 死亡筆記個陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a676ecfda3104b72d373ac87b6a73221d2932ea4","tid":219552,"uid":66580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T19:23:45.000Z","msg":"其實間間戲院都有老鼠<br />\n只係你唔會見到"},{"pid":"c9387ab9489ed96af21b4ee01430ea9504c1d056","tid":219552,"uid":38464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T19:31:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得幾好喎<br />\n戲飛平過ua一半，買盒叉雞飯入去食都無人理<br />\n係焗少少啫，咪張貨就價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n聽完你咁講更加唔想去"},{"pid":"eb207696b12312ec4dc7a897f273fa1ae4474924","tid":219552,"uid":25375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T19:34:28.000Z","msg":"喺手機睇都仲好過去巴倫紐睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"550a58d859358480f2f4983a7ce2fd43cd3be8e0","tid":219552,"uid":22938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T19:44:49.000Z","msg":"入去只係為咗溝女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"761c3af5900bec7a89130841d45e873c408139ff","tid":219552,"uid":41846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T20:04:27.000Z","msg":"咁平仲想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dfaaf66385e99b8ce2d0de9c0e15a34621bef2b","tid":219552,"uid":48675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T20:11:44.000Z","msg":"屯門ua淨係睇鬼片 好凍好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3867bf90ed56d9eba3663c8bf34e658028737bc","tid":219552,"uid":17551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T01:34:02.000Z","msg":"我覺得係d觀眾問題姐"},{"pid":"adac87b4bfb4c4540286f5f123ea3fb4b57c50fa","tid":219552,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T02:47:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得係d觀眾問題姐</blockquote><br />\n有人講野之類都係睇運<br />\n巴倫紐只係遇過一次開場播左分幾鐘就壞機，跟住出去退錢/換同價飛，但限1星期內用<br />\n同埋地板痴立立<br />\n其他真係冇咩好講，咁既價錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但家下有得揀都凱都<br />\n梯級位舒服得多"},{"pid":"35844cf27fc36190164d84c646a0be43f264ff54","tid":219552,"uid":66759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T02:47:51.000Z","msg":"體驗"}]}